
<%= render 'shared/header_all_pages' %>
    <section class="banner-area-product">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="main-div text-center">
              <div class="headline">
                <h1>SEAMLESS CAPITAL ACCESS</h1>
                <h1 class="color-orange">ONE APPLICATION. MULTIPLE OPTIONS.</h1>
              </div>

              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-yellow color-purple">
                <a href="#">APPLY TODAY</a>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="payment-terms-area bg-offwhite">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
          <div class="col-md-7 left-div order-two">
            <h1 class="h1-common">
              GET THE FUNDS YOU NEED WITH THE PAYMENT TERMS YOU WANT
            </h1>
            <p class="p-common mb-0">
              We know business cash flow is paramount, that's why we created
              three flexible types of cash you can access with our platform. By
              creating one profile, your application will be presented to
              multiple vendor partners eager to compete for your business. This
              enables you to spend time on your business, rather than raising
              money for it.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3 order-one">
            <div class="img-div">
              <%= image_tag("product/person.png", alt:"person") %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="business-area-product">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <h1 class="h1-common">
              EXPLORE OUR FUNDING SOLUTIONS FOR BUSINESS OWNERS
            </h1>
            <p class="p-common height-100 font-size-18">
              Seamless Capital Access offers three different options that will
              have terms specific to each funding partner, including:
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-90 justify-content-center">
          <div class="col-md-7 order-two">
            <div class="head-inner">
              SEAMLESS
              <span class="color-green"> ACH</span>
            </div>
            <p class="p-common">
              Seeking working capital with automated fixed repayment options and
              aggressive prepayment incentives? Seamless ACH offers funding
              options from $10,000 to $2,500,000 with daily, weekly and
              bi-weekly payment options*
            </p>
            <button class="btn btn-purple">APPLY TODAY</button>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3 order-one">
            <%= image_tag("ach.png", alt:"ach",:class => "float-right") %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-90 justify-content-center">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <%= image_tag("split.png", alt:"split",:class => "float-left") %>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-7">
            <div class="head-inner">
              SEAMLESS
              <span class="color-yellow"> SPLIT</span>
            </div>
            <p class="p-common">
              Would your business benefit from repayment flexibility based on
              future sales? Seamless Split offers funding options from $5,000 to
              $500,000 that fluctuate with the volatility of your daily credit
              card sales. Choose an option that works best for your business
              based on a small percentage of future credit card sales, and avoid
              fixed daily or weekly ACH payments.
            </p>
            <button class="btn btn-purple">APPLY TODAY</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-90 justify-content-center">
          <div class="col-md-7 order-two">
            <div class="head-inner">
              SEAMLESS
              <span class="color-orange"> EXPRESS</span>
            </div>
            <p class="p-common">
              We understand business demands change. Whether you are looking for
              relief from an unforeseen circumstance or capital to accelerate an
              opportunity, we've got you covered. Seamless Express offers
              $10,000 to $50,000 of immediate funding to help your business when
              you need it most. Fund as fast as 24 hours from application
              completion with minimal supporting documentation.
            </p>
            <button class="btn btn-purple">APPLY TODAY</button>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3 order-one">
            <%= image_tag("express.png", alt:"express",:class => "float-right") %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-90 justify-content-center">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <%= image_tag("zero.png", alt:"zero",:class => "float-left") %>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-7">
            <div class="head-inner">
              SEAMLESS
              <span class="color-purple"> ZERO</span>
            </div>
            <p class="p-common">
              Amidst the pressures of both a worldwide pandemic and inflation,
              our national businesses operate in unprecedented times. Business
              owners are faced with the daily challenge of providing exceptional
              products to their customers in a cost effective manner, without
              sacrificing any quality of service. At Seamless Capital Access, we
              share in the same vision and roadmap to your success. Seamless
              Zero allows merchants to simultaneously eliminate their processing
              fees for credit card acceptance while also providing their valued
              customers with an aggressive cash discount payment incentive. Shed
              the burden of costly credit card processing fees (and finance a
              portion or even all of your working capital funding) by
              integrating with SEAMLESS ZERO today!
            </p>
            <button class="btn btn-purple">APPLY TODAY</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

   

    <section class="guarantee-area bg-offwhite" >
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
          <div class="col-md-12">
          <!-- <h2 class="h2-common color-yellow mb-19">
